<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Holly Candy looked effortlessly chic on Thursday night as she enjoyed a night out with her husband Nick in Mayfair, London. </p>

<p>The Kiss Kiss hitmaker, 37, showcased her toned figure in a pair of stylish leather trousers and a sheer sparkly black top.</p>

<p>Adding some stylish accessories, Holly opted for a tailored dogtooth jacket with frayed hem detailing.</p>

<p>Chic: Holly Candy looked effortlessly chic on Thursday night as she enjoyed a night out with her husband Nick in Mayfair, London</p>

<p>Holly finished her look with dazzling diamond earrings, black heels and a sparkly clutch bag.</p>

<p>The former Neighbours actress styled her brunette locks into a sleek straightened hairdo and added a slick of radiant make-up.</p>

<p>Holly's husband Nick opted for a dapper blue trouser suit with a crisp unbuttoned white shirt for the outing. </p>

<p>The couple appeared in good spirits as they shared a giggle and walked hand-in-hand.</p>

<p>Date night: The Kiss Kiss hitmaker, 37, showcased her toned figure in a pair of stylish leather trousers and a sheer sparkly black top which she teamed with a tailored dogtooth jacket</p>

<p>Originally from Melbourne, Holly spent several years living in Los Angeles before settling down in London with billionaire property developer Nick.</p>

<p>The couple married back in September 2012 in a lavish ceremony held in Beverly Hills and are now parents to two daughters, Luka, six, and Nova, who turns three next month.</p>

<p>In 2019, former Neighbours star Holly spoke about motherhood and admitted she felt 'terrified' after giving birth to her eldest daughter.</p>

<p>Speaking during an interview on the Made By Mammas podcast, Holly said: 'At the beginning with Luka, I thought it was absolutely terrifying.</p>

<p>'It's like the best and worst thing to ever happen to you.'</p>

<p>She continued: 'It's terrifying. You're exploding with love but you don't know what you're doing. You're absolutely exhausted and fumbling around just trying to survive.'</p>

<p>Couple: Holly married Nick back in September 2012 in a lavish ceremony held in Beverly Hills and are now parents to two daughters, Luka, six, and Nova (pictured last year)</p>
